---------------------------------
**** A1)  toastr : 
---------------------------------
A1.1)
         in client dir : npm install ngx-toastr
A1.2)
         Add style to Angular.json -- section styles :
         "./node_modules/ngx-toastr/toastr.css"
---------------------------------
**** A2) angular guard auth template :

A2.1) 
        in client/src/app/_guards : ng g guard auth --skip-tests
A2.2)  
        select can activate (root)        

---------------------------------


---------------------------------
**** A3) add new theme from bootswatch.com
---------------------------------
A3.1)   
        Go To bootswatch.com
A3.2)
        in client dir : npm install bootswatch
A3.3)
        in angular.json add style of selected theme after datepicker:
        "./node_modules/bootswatch/dist/united/bootstrap.css"        
---------------------------------
**** A4) Shared Module
---------------------------------
A4.1)
        Create Folder in app : _modules
A4.2)
        go to _modules dir : ng g m shared --flat
A4.3) 
        cut those module from app.modul.ts
A4.4)  
        passed to shared , export those
A4.5)
        add sharedmodule to app.module.ts                            

---------------------------------
**** A5:  Restor Angular 
---------------------------------

For Restore Angular and all npm :

A5.1) npm instal
